78
00:06:15,809 --> 00:06:19,459
For they were able to play with
ideas… to explore them…

79
00:06:19,484 --> 00:06:23,984
not for any immediate practical
purpose but just for enjoyment.

80
00:06:24,576 --> 00:06:25,782
Play for its own sake.

81
00:06:27,242 --> 00:06:28,458
Now, about this mood.

82
00:06:29,248 --> 00:06:31,295
I’m working at the moment with
