uncultured dish is an irrelevance.

132
00:09:47,604 --> 00:09:50,778
In the open mode, it’s a clue.

133
00:09:51,431 --> 00:09:53,283
Now, one more example:

134
00:09:55,612 --> 00:09:59,399
