525
00:33:39,067 --> 00:33:42,783
And how they stop decisive,
hard-nosed bastards

526
00:33:42,784 --> 00:33:44,906
like us from running
businesses efficiently.

527
00:33:44,907 --> 00:33:46,651
I mean, we all know,

528
00:33:47,371 --> 00:33:49,433
we encourage someone
to be creative,

529
00:33:49,806 --> 00:33:51,416
the next thing is
they’re rocking

530
00:33:51,417 --> 00:33:53,774
the boat, coming up with
ideas, and asking us

531
00:33:53,775 --> 00:33:57,053
questions. Now, if we don’t nip
